      "question": "How do I apply for a rental property?",
      "answer": "Click the 'Apply Now' button on any property listing to start your application. You'll be directed to our screening partner where you can complete the application and background check."
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the application fee?",
      "answer": "Application fees vary by property but are typically $50. This covers the cost of credit and background checks and is non-refundable."
    },
    {
      "question": "Do you allow pets?",
      "answer": "Pet policies vary by property. Check each listing for specific pet policies. Some properties allow cats and dogs, while others may have restrictions."
    },
    {
      "question": "How much is the security deposit?",
      "answer": "Security deposits are typically equal to one month's rent. The exact amount is listed on each property page."
    },
    {
      "question": "When is rent due?",
      "answer": "Rent is due on the 1st of each month. Late fees may apply after a grace period as specified in your lease agreement."
    },
    {
      "question": "How do I schedule a property tour?",
      "answer": "Contact us via the contact form on any listing page or call our office during business hours to schedule a tour."
    }
